text: Reginald Edgecombe (1885 - 23 April 1966) was a British gymnast. He competed in the men's team all-around event at the 1920 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1885 births Category:1966 deaths Category:British male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Great Britain Category:Gymnasts at the 1920 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Birmingham, West Midlands
